songs.title: What You Tryna Do
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
If we can go out to an island, we can do whatever you want girl
I met her in LA, she was wildin'
She just tryna' get back, it's the time then
That girl so lovely, it's 3 in the morning
It must be something special
'Cause girl you know I'm on it

[Chorus]
You want me, I want you
You walkin', We got to
Why you actin'? You a bad ting'
If you walk by once, time's fast then
See you at the [?] you not cappin'
No, I'm not around, why you askin'?
On the hood, I ain't trippin' bout you
Baby show me, what you even tryna do

[Verse 2]
Since I got these racks, 'specially all these girls want me
Pull up in a demon, I skrt, yeah, you lucky
I just [?], got all these racks on me
Better watch your back, 'cause you lookin', that's on me
My bros hit the hoes for the party
I hit one time, say you want me
She said I couldn't [?], didn't stop me
And sometimes be off lean, I'm feelin' lonely

[Chorus]
You want me, I want you
You walkin', We got to
Why you actin'? You a bad ting'
If you walk by once, time's fast then
See you at the [?] you not cappin'
No, I'm not around, why you askin'?
On the hood, I ain't trippin' bout you
Baby show me, what you even tryna do
